Package: tsbiomass
Title: TS Biomass Model Transferability Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bundles the TS-model transferability workflow, benchmark logic,
    admissibility screening, uncertainty benchmarking, sensitivity analyses,
    and figure-generation pipeline used for TS-to-biomass transfer analyses.
    The package is configuration-driven and can be run from YAML/JSON workflow
    files or from the preserved command-line interface.
